com.github.davidmoten.grumpy.util

Class NearBSpline

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.davidmoten.grumpy.util.NearBSpline
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Shape, Cloneable

    public class NearBSpline
extends Object
implements Shape, Cloneable
    A shape that is almost a B-spline curve but not necessarily exactly. If the shape has n points, the following things are guaranteed:
    • n == 2: the shape is a straight line,
    • n == 3: the shape is a quadratic curve,
    • n == 4: the shape is a cubic curve,
    • n >= 5: the shape consists of segments, which are joined together so that the first derivate is continuous at intermittent points
